Features:

This block gives you the ability to search through the libroslibres site 
(http://libroslibres.flacso.org.ar)

Installation:

1- Place the libroslibres folder (if you have downloaded zipped then you have to unzip 
it) into the blocks folder under the root of your Moodle installation.
2- Go to the notifications page and Moodle will automatically install this new
block. 
3- Turn Editing on and add the block "Libros Libres search box". 
4- That's it. Enjoy it!
 
